Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.74,0:23:07.98,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無重力的暗閻　唯有摸索前行
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.33,0:23:10.77,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMS Gothic}Where do we go?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.62,0:23:19.38,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如同莫比烏斯環一般　命運九轉輪迴
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.38,0:23:22.21,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMS Gothic\fsp0.1}Win, Lose Or Draw
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.09,0:23:28.18,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真實究竟何在{\fnMS Gothic}？ {\fsp0}Lies & Truth
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.51,0:23:34.42,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光影回轉{\fsp-9}　{\fsp1.5}陰陽相生
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.42,0:23:39.38,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命運之骰一經擲出　就已無法停止轉動
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.65,0:23:42.37,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMS Gothic\fsp0}Dive into the Light
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.19,0:23:50.78,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毀滅之風揚　我只欲逆風直上
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.78,0:23:53.71,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將你緊緊擁入懷抱中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.12,0:24:01.80,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,制裁之劍{\fsp-9}　{\fsp1.5}斬斷這一昏暗的時代
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.80,0:24:08.26,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獨彷徨　{\fnMS Gothic\fsp0}Lost In Space
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【Main】
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.00,0:01:41.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重要的要塞落於敵手 臣愧對殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.50,0:01:46.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1110,923)\fad(500,500)}哲力胥·泰坦尼亞公爵
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.50,0:01:46.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1110,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}ザーリッシュ・タイタニア公爵
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.19,0:01:43.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是臣力排眾議 獨力承擔的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.30,0:01:45.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果卻落得如此下場
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.06,0:01:50.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臣甘願領罰
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.11,0:01:53.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(807,923)\fad(500,500)}無地藩王 亞術曼·泰坦尼亞
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.11,0:01:53.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(807,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}無地藩王 アジュマーン・タイタニア
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.87,0:01:52.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藩王殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.25,0:01:58.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1281,923)\fad(500,500)}亞歷亞伯特·泰坦尼亞公爵
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.25,0:01:58.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1281,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}アリアバート・タイタニア公爵
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.87,0:01:56.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我軍駐守部隊僅有區區三百艘
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.64,0:01:59.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵方十倍於我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.35,0:02:03.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(609,923)\fad(500,500)}褚士朗·泰坦尼亞公爵
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.35,0:02:03.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(609,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}ジュスラン・タイタニア公爵
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.45,0:02:01.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很難取得勝利
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.55,0:02:02.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可未必
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.42,0:02:08.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1281,923)\fad(500,500)}伊德里斯·泰坦尼亞公爵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.42,0:02:08.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1281,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}イドリス・タイタニア公爵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.86,0:02:07.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以寡擊眾的先例並不少見
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.34,0:02:11.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我方太大意了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.52,0:02:15.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣說來 大家都有責任
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.95,0:02:20.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眾卿好像誤會了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.63,0:02:24.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此事對泰坦尼亞有益無害
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.23,0:02:28.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海賊此後的動向呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.10,0:02:29.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.01,0:02:35.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海賊們數量愈增愈多
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.81,0:02:38.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在要塞周圍集結
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.38,0:02:41.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總數恐怕不下五千艘
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.56,0:02:44.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真虧他們能聚集這麼多
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.82,0:02:45.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說是海賊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.18,0:02:48.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但若聚成集團 倒也不可小覷
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.63,0:02:51.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.16,0:02:55.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此舉無疑於自掘墳墓
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.01,0:03:03.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好趁此良機一舉斬斷禍根 去除後患
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.14,0:03:04.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藩王殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.01,0:03:08.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還請允許我將功補過
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.72,0:03:10.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.04,0:03:11.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.51,0:03:13.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,褚士朗卿
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.70,0:03:14.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.02,0:03:18.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命你作為副司令輔佐哲力胥卿
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.87,0:03:21.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.04,0:03:36.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(571,290)\fad(500,500)\fs90\bord4}兩場邂逅
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.58,0:03:40.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,923)\fad(500,500)}惑星卡嘉諾特 流星旗軍基地
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.58,0:03:40.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}惑星カガノート 流星旗軍基地
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.21,0:03:40.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,流星旗軍也蠻能幹的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.72,0:03:44.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定能行得通哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.87,0:03:52.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲 方修利提督
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.21,0:03:53.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.31,0:03:55.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,補給還順利吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.32,0:03:58.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托你的福 多謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.37,0:04:03.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1403,923)\fad(500,500)}米蘭達·卡西米爾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.37,0:04:03.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1403,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}ミランダ・カジミール
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.90,0:04:01.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橫看豎看 這艘船還是這麼老
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.42,0:04:03.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真虧它還能動
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.67,0:04:06.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們保養得好 船長的技術也沒得說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.63,0:04:11.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但作為方修利提督的座駕還略嫌不足
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.65,0:04:16.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(600,923)\fad(500,500)}道爾曼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.65,0:04:16.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(600,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}}ドールマン
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.56,0:04:17.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是我的話 就準備最新型的艦艇
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.28,0:04:23.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實我想向提督引薦幾個人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.50,0:04:26.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1116,923)\fad(500,500)}方修利
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.50,0:04:26.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1116,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}ファン・ヒューリック
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.98,0:04:25.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能勞您大駕嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.97,0:04:30.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我介紹一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.19,0:04:33.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這位是原提蘭基亞軍的漢力克少將
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.10,0:04:35.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.78,0:04:39.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(855,923)\fad(500,500)}漢力克少將
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.78,0:04:39.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(855,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}ヘンリック少将
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.63,0:04:38.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能拜見凱貝羅斯會戰英雄的尊容
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.89,0:04:39.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不勝榮幸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.58,0:04:44.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(552,923)\fad(500,500)}托斯卡尼少將
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.58,0:04:44.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(543,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}トスカーニ少将
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.58,0:04:44.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1274,923)\fad(500,500)}馬凱澤中將
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.58,0:04:44.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1274,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}マッケンゼン中将
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.23,0:04:40.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.02,0:04:43.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬凱澤中將和托斯卡尼少將
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.17,0:04:44.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.49,0:04:47.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家看起來都不怎麼像海賊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.14,0:04:49.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幾位都是正統軍人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.07,0:04:52.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為箇中原因 不便透漏國家的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.30,0:04:58.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然特地當逃兵 真辛苦你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.97,0:05:02.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎麼憎恨泰坦尼亞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.81,0:05:05.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正規軍怎麼會幫海賊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.46,0:05:06.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.54,0:05:08.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提督說得不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.30,0:05:09.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這次不必擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.99,0:05:13.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不會重蹈艾里亞和提蘭基亞的覆轍
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.63,0:05:14.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有何根據？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.98,0:05:16.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們攻佔要塞後
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.51,0:05:18.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,援軍正源源趕來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.08,0:05:25.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其數可達五千艘以上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.76,0:05:29.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有方修利提督率軍 豈不是所向披靡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.14,0:05:33.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡人才濟濟 根本輪不到我出場嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.58,0:05:37.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了振奮士氣 英雄是不可或缺的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.27,0:05:42.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還請和我們攜手 再次擊破泰坦尼亞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.96,0:05:46.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你意下如何 提督
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.51,0:05:49.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我考慮一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.22,0:05:53.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不答應
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.28,0:05:56.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可是大艦隊的總司令耶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.11,0:06:02.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就甘心永遠坐著那艘破船航行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.57,0:06:03.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船破了點 不好意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.69,0:06:06.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼時候能完成補給
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.88,0:06:09.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.52,0:06:11.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.83,0:06:17.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也該告辭了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.62,0:06:20.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.44,0:06:21.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有流星旗軍在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.82,0:06:23.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們就不用東躲西藏了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.91,0:06:25.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們沒有勝算
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.79,0:06:26.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可是五千艘耶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.42,0:06:29.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是連泰坦尼亞的要塞都打下來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.89,0:06:31.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒼蠅這東西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.36,0:06:35.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若一隻隻解決根本沒完沒了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.80,0:06:38.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但它們若全部聚集到一處呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.59,0:06:42.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.10,0:06:49.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,923)\fad(500,500)}艾賓格王國
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.10,0:06:49.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}エルビング王国
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.96,0:07:02.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真煞風景
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.07,0:07:05.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺 那艘船是幹什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.02,0:07:08.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是泰坦尼亞的軍艦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.80,0:07:12.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說是從要塞逃出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.57,0:07:15.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,923)\fad(500,500)}艾賓格王國 第二公主莉迪亞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.57,0:07:15.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}エルビング王国 第二王女リディア
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.07,0:07:15.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是泰坦尼亞嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.75,0:07:20.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不巧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.76,0:07:23.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然逃到我國…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.10,0:07:26.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.90,0:07:28.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把他們趕走不就得了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.85,0:07:30.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說他們有傷員
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.75,0:07:33.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,國王陛下也思量再三
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.59,0:07:36.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果還是同意他們入境了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.30,0:07:38.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.96,0:07:40.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.11,0:07:43.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若私藏泰坦尼亞軍隊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.82,0:07:45.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會被流星旗軍盯上的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.78,0:07:48.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不就是個區區海賊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.85,0:07:52.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不 他們攻陷了泰坦尼亞要塞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.58,0:07:54.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其氣勢不可小覷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.04,0:07:59.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說現在支配這片星域的是他們也不為過
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.71,0:08:05.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但泰坦尼亞也不會坐視不理的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.08,0:08:07.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話雖如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.05,0:08:12.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺比起泰坦尼亞更怕海賊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.86,0:08:16.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個問題我很難回答
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.60,0:08:21.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我認為父皇是對的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.61,0:08:33.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,923)\fad(500,500)}哲力胥艦隊旗艦 颱風
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.61,0:08:33.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}ザーリッシュ艦隊旗艦 タイフーン
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.50,0:08:37.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是將討厭的蒼蠅一網打盡的絕佳良機
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.75,0:08:40.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還請諸位全力以赴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.42,0:08:47.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說藩王殿下為什麼要指派我…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.53,0:08:51.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(803,803)\fad(500,500)\fs40}Uraniberg
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.53,0:08:51.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,878)\fad(500,500)}天城 休憩圓頂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.53,0:08:51.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(727,918)\fad(500,500)\fs31\fnms gothic}ウラニボルグ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.53,0:08:51.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,988)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}天の城 ラウンジドーム
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.84,0:08:52.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,論率兵打仗 應該是你比較在行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.23,0:08:57.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若由我擔任副將 哲力胥會綁手綁腳
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.97,0:09:03.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊德里斯卿還有近衛軍司令的任務在身
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.95,0:09:06.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.78,0:09:08.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,褚士朗閣下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.87,0:09:12.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藩王殿下有請
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.96,0:09:13.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.90,0:09:16.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.47,0:09:21.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此行多半能解開你心頭的疑問
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.13,0:09:31.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,褚士朗 前來報到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.86,0:09:37.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道艾斯特拉德·泰坦尼亞侯爵吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.27,0:09:39.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.53,0:09:41.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是殿下的兄長
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.26,0:09:44.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現任維爾達納帝國軍務大臣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.19,0:09:46.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.56,0:09:51.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他正陰謀把我從藩王寶座上趕下來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.26,0:09:57.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這多半是破壞我族團結的流言吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.71,0:09:59.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那當然
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.99,0:10:02.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但也不可小看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.69,0:10:06.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊德里斯卿似乎極為肯定
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.94,0:10:08.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊德里斯卿？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.43,0:10:13.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你認為他會無中生有嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.33,0:10:13.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.60,0:10:18.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維爾納達的宮廷貴族若要作亂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.34,0:10:20.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必然會慫恿艾斯特拉德
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.20,0:10:24.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若是我 就會這樣做
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.67,0:10:26.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.87,0:10:28.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若平白無故地處分軍務大臣…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.24,0:10:32.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反而會讓親者痛 仇者快
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.65,0:10:35.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾斯特拉德閣下可是泰坦尼亞的重要人物
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.54,0:10:40.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就讓鼠輩們高興兩天也無妨
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.42,0:10:41.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殿下 那可…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.27,0:10:46.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在不需要馬上動手
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.19,0:10:51.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當前只需防止傷口擴大
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.52,0:10:57.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,褚士朗卿聽旨
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.56,0:11:02.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孤命你帶法爾密子爵為高級副官共赴戰場
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.24,0:11:05.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,軍務大臣的公子…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.79,0:11:07.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要把他挾做人質嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.93,0:11:09.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也是一方面
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.37,0:11:12.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臣遵旨
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.90,0:11:16.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,願收法爾密子爵為我的高級副官
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.04,0:11:17.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,退下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.91,0:11:18.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.71,0:11:24.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不惜犧牲自己的哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.02,0:11:27.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也要將帝國內的敵人一掃而光
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.39,0:11:30.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一決斷聽來有些悲壯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.96,0:11:37.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前提是哥哥沒有取代弟弟的資格…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.52,0:11:57.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下就是本次受命擔任閣下副官的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.11,0:11:59.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1313,855)\fad(500,500)}法爾密·泰坦尼亞子爵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.11,0:11:59.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1313,925)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}バルアミー・タイタニア子爵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.78,0:11:59.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法爾密·泰坦尼亞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.08,0:12:01.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多指教 法爾密卿
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.43,0:12:03.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問我該如何稱呼您
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.84,0:12:06.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公爵閣下 還是上將閣下？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.79,0:12:12.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我該叫你子爵閣下 不 准將閣下？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.93,0:12:15.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能請您不要這樣稱呼我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.36,0:12:19.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你也叫我褚士朗卿好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.35,0:12:20.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必拘於禮節
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.84,0:12:23.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恕在下冒昧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.04,0:12:26.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所謂副官應當做些什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.89,0:12:28.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.61,0:12:29.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.47,0:12:33.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討伐軍總司令是哲力胥卿
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.86,0:12:35.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他強到沒話說
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.97,0:12:37.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本不用我出場
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.47,0:12:42.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哲力胥卿只是為褚士朗卿墊場的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.57,0:12:47.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來法爾密卿喜歡挑撥離間呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.06,0:12:49.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不敢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.72,0:12:51.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,承蒙你如此之高的評價 我很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.69,0:12:53.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但人各有志
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.61,0:12:56.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法爾密卿
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.89,0:12:57.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.00,0:13:00.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艦隊正在準備出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.49,0:13:03.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你先去晨曦女神等我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.63,0:13:04.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.90,0:13:10.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芙蘭西亞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.19,0:13:12.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 褚士朗大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.69,0:13:15.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1065,923)\fad(500,500)}芙蘭西亞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.69,0:13:15.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1065,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}フランシア
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.52,0:13:18.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來大家都有些高估我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.17,0:13:19.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.40,0:13:26.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵我雙方都是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.52,0:13:34.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有幾個國家不願加入我們
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.79,0:13:39.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾賓格王國還藏有泰坦尼亞的逃兵
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.37,0:13:41.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攘外必先安內
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.04,0:13:43.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要派兵前往嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.87,0:13:47.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種窮國 下官三兩下就能…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.46,0:13:49.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也很想這樣做…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.58,0:13:51.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泰坦尼亞有所行動了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.55,0:13:54.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艦艇一萬兩千艘
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.75,0:13:58.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指揮官似乎是哲力胥·泰坦尼亞公爵
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.01,0:14:03.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,數量是我軍的一倍以上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.37,0:14:06.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 若是猛將哲力胥帶兵的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.61,0:14:08.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其破壞力會加成數倍
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.61,0:14:12.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 不必擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.78,0:14:15.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以寡擊眾的戰例數不勝數
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.67,0:14:19.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 我們還有方修利
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.87,0:14:21.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我軍風頭正勁
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.87,0:14:25.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再加上方修利提督運籌帷幄…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.04,0:14:28.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.67,0:14:30.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.50,0:14:34.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.73,0:14:37.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出什麼事了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.62,0:14:39.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.67,0:14:40.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.97,0:14:42.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方修利嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.46,0:14:43.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.08,0:14:45.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得馬上把他帶回來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.98,0:14:46.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快下令
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.34,0:14:48.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用管他
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.66,0:14:51.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個一心想逃的男人能有什麼用
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.23,0:14:53.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有我們在就足夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.16,0:14:55.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.23,0:14:56.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們聽我說
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.56,0:15:02.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,little-big-horn要塞在天城建成以前
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.12,0:15:04.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可列入三大巨型建築物之列
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.79,0:15:07.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是重要文化遺產
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.25,0:15:14.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同時 這一要塞也是泰坦尼亞的重要軍事據點
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.25,0:15:18.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哲力胥的目的必然是奪回要塞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.85,0:15:22.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 我們佈陣時就以此為盾
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.87,0:15:24.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要全員困守要塞嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.31,0:15:26.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.77,0:15:31.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要這樣背臨要塞布下密集陣形
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.36,0:15:35.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們生怕傷到要塞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.45,0:15:37.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攻擊時難免畏首畏尾
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.11,0:15:39.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時機一到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.54,0:15:41.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就由機動隊將其一網打盡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.32,0:15:44.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是所謂的刺蝟戰術嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.20,0:15:46.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們佔有地利
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.14,0:15:49.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算對手是哲力胥 我們也不會輸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.53,0:15:54.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就當方修利沒來過
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.71,0:15:56.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.99,0:15:57.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.65,0:16:34.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發現敵方據點
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.32,0:16:35.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顯示影像
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.46,0:16:49.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自作聰明
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.86,0:16:54.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人似乎打算負隅頑抗呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.67,0:16:56.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泰坦尼亞開始進攻了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.30,0:16:58.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按作戰計劃行事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.02,0:17:00.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.54,0:17:08.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全艦徑直前行 不准減速
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.26,0:17:12.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去 要塞會被打得千瘡百孔的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.46,0:17:13.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.89,0:17:16.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可是我們重要的軍事據點
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.47,0:17:19.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要塞被奪乃泰坦尼亞之恥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.85,0:17:22.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若能藉此將蒼蠅一網打盡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.97,0:17:25.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一兩個要塞算不了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.17,0:17:33.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵軍並未減速
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.91,0:17:35.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全軍一併向這邊衝過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.56,0:17:43.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發現伏兵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.81,0:17:46.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Point Z02和M62
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.86,0:17:49.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,派第一第三分隊前去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.60,0:17:56.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵艦隊 二十秒內到達要塞
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.81,0:17:59.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.07,0:18:02.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全艦突擊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.42,0:18:17.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向全軍下令 作戰計劃有變
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.53,0:18:18.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把馬凱澤給我叫來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.01,0:18:20.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰艦斯凱拉 失去聯繫
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.02,0:18:21.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.04,0:18:24.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬凱澤提督也戰死了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.58,0:18:27.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬凱澤…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.82,0:18:40.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰艦特塞斯被擊沉了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.94,0:18:42.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漢力克少將戰死
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.07,0:18:44.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托斯卡尼艦隊全滅
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.48,0:18:46.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵艦隊衝過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.07,0:18:51.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,投降
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.28,0:18:53.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向哲力胥閣下請降
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.20,0:18:55.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真符合哲力胥卿的作風
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.60,0:18:59.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然沒有我出場的餘地
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.81,0:19:06.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,923)\fad(500,500)}「正直老人」號
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.81,0:19:06.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}「正直じいさん」号
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.58,0:19:09.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我早就想會會你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.39,0:19:11.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方修利提督
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.24,0:19:15.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就知道咱們還能見面
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.35,0:19:18.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1265,923)\fad(500,500)}李博士
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.35,0:19:18.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1265,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}ドクター・リー
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.03,0:19:16.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,李博士
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.58,0:19:18.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還能？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.76,0:19:20.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 還能
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.13,0:19:24.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,流星旗軍似乎全軍覆滅了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.71,0:19:26.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是理所當然的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.72,0:19:29.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰讓他們不聽我的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.18,0:19:32.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說來 我們算是撿了一條命咯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.08,0:19:35.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關鍵是你能拿這條命做點什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.59,0:19:36.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若拿來虛度時光的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.97,0:19:38.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就沒什麼意義了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.68,0:19:40.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你討厭泰坦尼亞嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.97,0:19:43.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泰坦尼亞是全宇宙最強大的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.56,0:19:44.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我不喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.69,0:19:49.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僅此而已 泰坦尼亞沒有責任
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.62,0:19:52.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你認為自己能滅亡泰坦尼亞嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.68,0:19:54.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕很難
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.80,0:19:58.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但今後可能會出現轉機
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.97,0:20:02.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近發生了幾件前所未有的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.50,0:20:04.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如說？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.87,0:20:10.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泰坦尼亞四公爵之一不可能被一國艦隊打敗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.10,0:20:13.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在座的這位完成了這一壯舉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.54,0:20:17.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以認為你是在表揚我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.04,0:20:20.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是在貶低泰坦尼亞罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.02,0:20:25.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.93,0:20:27.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但可能性還是有的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.20,0:20:29.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.19,0:20:31.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變革的可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.29,0:20:35.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,動搖泰坦尼亞霸權的變革浪潮
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.16,0:20:38.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是個天才 我承認
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.02,0:20:44.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不錯嘛 能受到李博士這麼高的評價
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.52,0:20:45.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.89,0:20:48.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個男人真有這麼大的價值嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.81,0:20:50.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提督個人沒有價值
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.35,0:20:54.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他所持有的變革可能性才有價值
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.87,0:20:56.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我問你一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.48,0:21:00.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提督恨泰坦尼亞嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.97,0:21:10.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1274,923)\fad(500,500)}艾賓格王國國王
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.97,0:21:10.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1274,993)\fad(500,500)\fs62\fnms gothic}エルビング王国国王
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.08,0:21:08.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父皇大人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.06,0:21:11.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉迪亞嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.66,0:21:13.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您有什麼煩惱嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.78,0:21:14.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泰坦尼亞贏了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.15,0:21:18.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父皇的判斷沒有錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.17,0:21:23.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泰坦尼亞沒有怪罪我們
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.13,0:21:25.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.86,0:21:30.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泰坦尼亞要我國將能量礦山交給他們
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.70,0:21:34.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以示忠誠
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.06,0:21:39.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去那座礦山的話
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.38,0:21:43.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整個國家都會破產的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.77,0:21:46.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們在考驗我們的忠誠
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.79,0:21:49.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們無法違逆泰坦尼亞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.89,0:21:52.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但如此一來 百姓的生活…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.91,0:22:03.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父皇大人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.32,0:22:06.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.58,0:22:08.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莉迪亞
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.51,0:22:13.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要證明我們別無二心就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.09,0:22:17.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就由我 莉迪亞去當人質吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.56,0:22:18.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主大人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.01,0:22:22.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我早就想去天城玩玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.72,0:22:24.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可… 公主大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.29,0:22:28.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也想見見傳說中的四公爵
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.96,0:22:34.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是一股微不足道的新風
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.17,0:22:41.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但它將為泰坦尼亞注入全新的某物
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.30,0:24:17.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主大人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.30,0:24:18.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您真要去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.32,0:24:22.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臣聽說天城是個可怕的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.52,0:24:24.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主真是太勇敢了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.02,0:24:27.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺 爺爺我…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.03,0:24:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(644,290)\fad(500,0)\fs90\bord5}微小的新風


